<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="154" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,151,573]" pageId="12" pageNumber="154">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,187,213]" pageId="12" pageNumber="154">Etymology</emphasis>
The epithet of this new species (Latin adjective 
<emphasis box="[879,989,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="154">capillatus</emphasis>
